General
- Everything (code, comments, docs, commits) must be in English.
- Keep the architecture simple and easy to understand.
- Prefer readability over clever or complex solutions.

Code
- Follow standard style conventions (PEP8 for Python).
- Use clear, descriptive names.
- Keep functions and modules small and focused.
- Add short docstrings when helpful.

Dependencies
- Only add dependencies when necessary.
- Document any required environment variables or external services.
